Dialogue: 0,00:19:30.31,00:19:31.07,hibiya ch,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,00:19:31.80,00:19:34.13,hiyori ch,,0,0,0,,不过 我不讨厌夏天哦
Dialogue: 0,00:19:34.59,00:19:37.24,hibiya ch,,0,0,0,,我 讨厌夏天
Dialogue: 0,00:19:44.35,00:19:45.33,hibiya ch,,0,0,0,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,00:20:12.38,00:20:13.76,hibiya ch,,0,0,0,,得逞不了了吧
